Like all centers of wealth and prosperity, Chiiron has attracted its<br>
share of those that would prey upon those who have wealth and happiness. <br>
Bandits have taken refuge in the hills to the south of Chiiron.  The<br>
reports of their numbers and strength vary, and the Guardsmen and Mages<br>
are unable to devote time to tracking them down.<br>
